Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before moving to any next activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total resolution time of cases starting with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time for cases that involve 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' more than once before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle Time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' directly follows it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to understand vendor-related delays
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' to assess the impact on customer satisfaction
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
